Made this recipe for tonight's Thanksgiving dinner. It was a huge hit. I used sweet Turkey sausage. Also, as per another reviewer, I did add craisins. The flavor was great and it also added some color to the presentation. Looks a bit "beige" otherwise. Additionally, I chopped some flat parsley and added that as well. Nice color and flavor. FANTASTIC!

